An Act relating to veterans; requiring the Oklahoma
7
Department of Veterans Affairs to create certain
8
program to provide certain headstone or marker;
8
providing certain requirements for certain headstone
9
or marker; providing certain burial grant for certain
9
eligible persons; providing certain eligibility
10
requirements; requiring certain promulgation of
10
rules; creating certain revolving fund; providing for
11
